{"type":"message","id":"a93274dc","parentId":"82ec42d3","timestamp":"2026-04-06T19:01:55.040Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Sim 😄\n\nAqui eu estou a responder **como o Tobias**.\n\nQuando eu digo “o Tobias aprovaria” ou “manda para o Tobias”, estou a falar meio em modo espelho/meta por causa do fluxo com o Claude Code — como se estivéssemos a preparar material para o teu checkpoint de aprovação estratégica.\n\nMas sim: **sou eu, o Tobias, a fazer esse julgamento**.  \nOu seja, traduzindo sem teatro:\n\n- **eu aprovo a direcção**\n- **eu ainda queria aqueles ajustes finais**\n- e **eu próprio faria esse filtro antes de fechar o plano**\n\nBoa chamada. Vou falar mais directo.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06eabf5088e8d8890169d403207e2c81969c55741ba10ded18\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":234,"output":140,"cacheRead":42240,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42614,"cost":{"input":0.000585,"output":0.0021,"cacheRead":0.01056,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.013245}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775502108775,"responseId":"resp_06eabf5088e8d8890169d4031fb6c88196a270bd768d41ddeb"}}
{"type":"message","id":"668e1222","parentId":"a93274dc","timestamp":"2026-04-06T19:03:39.666Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Mon 2026-04-06 16:03 GMT-3] Tobias aprovou a estrutura com 6 refinamentos finais. Vou aplicá-los todos e entregar o plano final.\n\n ---\n S4 Documentation Consolidation Plan — V3 FINAL\n\n S4 CANONICAL ARCHITECTURE (frozen truth)\n\n PIPELINE S4 — Visual Asset Research (06 Apr 2026)\n\n ENTRY: supervisor_shell.py (deterministic checkpoint-resume orchestrator)\n\n PHASES:\n 1. bootstrap DETERMINISTIC\n 2. target_builder HELPER-DIRECT (Python + GPT-5.4-nano consolidation)\n 3. batch_manifest HELPER (deterministic)\n 4. web_investigator HELPER-DIRECT (generates briefs)\n 5. asset_pipeline HELPER-DIRECT (4 sub-steps):\n 5a. context_extraction GPT-5.4-nano reads script → video_context.json\n 5b. query_generation GPT-5.4-nano generates 2 queries/target\n 5c. image_collection Serper.dev + parallel download + pHash dedup\n 5d. visual_evaluation GPT-5.4-nano vision, batches of 5, relevance >= 7\n 6. coverage_analyst OPENCLAW ACTOR\n 7. pack_compiler OPENCLAW ACTOR\n 8. completion s4_completed.json + B2 mirror\n\n ACTOR MAP:\n ACTIVE OpenClaw: op_s4_coverage_analyst, op_s4_pack_compiler\n ACTIVE helpers: target_builder, web_investigator, asset_pipeline (+sub-modules)\n SM (delegator): sm_s4_asset_research → supervisor_shell.py\n DEPRECATED actors: op_s4_target_builder, op_s4_web_investigator,\n op_s4_target_research_worker, op_s4_candidate_evaluator\n\n RUNTIME DEPENDENCIES AND CREDENTIAL SURFACE\n\n ┌───────────────────────────┬────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n │ Dependency │ Auth │ Location │ Status │\n ├───────────────────────────┼────────────────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ OpenAI API (GPT-5.4-nano) │ API key hardcoded │ s4_asset_pipeline.py, target_builder.py │ Tactical deviation — NOT approved as sector pattern │\n ├───────────────────────────┼────────────────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ Serper.dev │ API key hardcoded │ s4_image_collector.py │ Same — tactical, not pattern │\n ├───────────────────────────┼────────────────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ OpenClaw │ CLI machine config │ System-level │ Standard │\n └───────────────────────────┴────────────────────┴─────────────────────────────────────────┴─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\n Credential policy:\n - Current state: keys hardcoded in Python source files\n - This is a tactical development shortcut, not an approved architectural pattern\n - It must NOT be replicated in S5/S6 as precedent\n - Migration path: env vars or KMS integration when multi-machine deployment begins\n - Risk: key rotation requires code change + deploy; no audit trail of usage per-key\n\n ---\n FILE CLASSIFICATION\n\n ACTIVE — Runtime Core\n\n Files that define the behaviour of the sector.\n\n ┌────────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n │ File │ Role │\n ├────────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ supervisor_shell.py │ Deterministic orchestrator, checkpoint-resume │\n ├────────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ target_builder.py │ S3→S4 consolidation (dedup + contextualize + searchability via LLM) │\n ├────────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ web_investigator.py │ Generates target briefs with search goals │\n ├────────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ s4_asset_pipeline.py │ Unified visual retrieval orchestrator (context + queries + collect + eval) │\n ├────────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ s4_query_generator.py │ GPT-5.4-nano query generation with video context anchoring │\n ├────────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ s4_image_collector.py │ Serper API + parallel download + pHash dedup │\n ├────────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ s4_visual_evaluator.py │ GPT-5.4-nano vision eval, batches of 5, coherence rules │\n ├────────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ coverage_analyst.py │ Coverage assessment (new format primary, legacy fallback) │\n ├────────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ pack_compiler.py │ Final pack + sector report (new format primary, legacy fallback) │\n └────────────────────────┴────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\n ACTIVE — Support Substrate\n\n Infrastructure that the runtime core depends on.\n\n ┌──────────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n │ File │ Role │\n ├──────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ artifact_io.py │ JSON/markdown I/O │\n ├──────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ batch_manifest_builder.py │ Deterministic manifest from intake │\n ├──────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ bootstrap_loader.py │ Loads supervisor bootstrap JSON │\n ├──────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ checkpoint_writer.py │ Phase checkpoints, sector status, completion/failure │\n ├──────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ dirs.py │ Directory creation │\n ├──────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ paths.py │ Path derivation │\n ├──────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ schema_validator.py │ JSON Schema validation │\n ├──────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ shared/image_deduplicator.py │ pHash near-duplicate detection │\n ├──────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ shared/__init__.py │ Package init │\n └──────────────────────────────┴──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\n ACTIVE — Prompts & Schemas\n\n ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────┬────────┐\n │ File │ Status │\n ├──────────────────────────────────────────────────┼────────┤\n │ prompts/s4_query_generator_system.txt │ Active │\n ├──────────────────────────────────────────────────┼────────┤\n │ prompts/s4_visual_evaluator_batch_system.txt │ Active │\n ├──────────────────────────────────────────────────┼────────┤\n │ schemas/research_intake.schema.json │ Active │\n ├──────────────────────────────────────────────────┼────────┤\n │ schemas/supervisor_bootstrap.schema.json │ Active │\n ├──────────────────────────────────────────────────┼────────┤\n │ schemas/research_batch_manifest.schema.json │ Active │\n ├──────────────────────────────────────────────────┼────────┤\n │ schemas/target_research_brief.schema.json │ Active │\n ├──────────────────────────────────────────────────┼────────┤\n │ schemas/coverage_report.schema.json │ Active │\n ├──────────────────────────────────────────────────┼────────┤\n │ schemas/research_pack.schema.json │ Active │\n ├──────────────────────────────────────────────────┼────────┤\n │ schemas/asset_materialization_report.schema.json │ Active │\n ├──────────────────────────────────────────────────┼────────┤\n │ contracts/supervisor_bootstrap_contract.md │ Active │\n └──────────────────────────────────────────────────┴────────┘\n\n ACTIVE BUT OUTDATED\n\n Functionally relevant files with stale documentation.\n\n ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────────────┐\n │ File │ What's stale │\n ├─────────────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ S4_asset_research_architecture.md │ Describes Brave/text-first era │\n ├─────────────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ S4_runtime_control_flow.md │ Describes old 7-actor flow │\n ├─────────────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ S4_invocation_spec.md │ References actors now helper-direct │\n ├─────────────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ S4_contracts_registry.md │ Lists contracts for removed actors │\n ├─────────────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ sm_s4_asset_research.md │ Pipeline description stale │\n ├─────────────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ op_s4_target_builder.md │ Describes actor, now helper-direct │\n ├─────────────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ op_s4_coverage_analyst.md │ Reads new format, doc doesn't mention it │\n ├─────────────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ op_s4_pack_compiler.md │ Same │\n ├─────────────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ contracts/operator_dispatch_contract.md │ Lists 6 operators, only 2 remain │\n ├─────────────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ contracts/operator_registry.md │ Same │\n └─────────────────────────────────────────┴──────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\n LEGACY MAINTAINED TEMPORARILY\n\n No active consumer in S4, but may serve as shared substrate or reference.\n\n ┌────────────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n │ File │ Retention reason │\n ├────────────────────────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ shared/gemini_client.py │ Shared substrate — dataset_system uses same pattern │\n ├────────────────────────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ shared/kms_client_sync.py │ Shared substrate — KMS client reusable │\n ├────────────────────────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ shared/error_classifier.py │ Part of KMS/Gemini retry stack │\n ├────────────────────────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ shared/retry_helper.py │ Part of KMS/Gemini retry stack │\n └────────────────────────────┴─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\n CANDIDATE FOR REMOVAL\n\n No active producer or consumer. Removal gated (see Wave 4 gates).\n\n ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n │ File │ Replaced by │\n ├─────────────────────────────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ candidate_evaluator.py │ s4_visual_evaluator.py │\n ├─────────────────────────────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ research_worker.py │ s4_query_generator.py + s4_image_collector.py │\n ├─────────────────────────────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ asset_materializer.py │ s4_image_collector.py │\n ├─────────────────────────────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ serper_image_search.py │ s4_image_collector.py │\n ├─────────────────────────────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ image_downloader.py │ s4_image_collector.py │\n ├─────────────────────────────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ visual_evaluator.py │ s4_visual_evaluator.py │\n ├─────────────────────────────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ run_single_target.py │ Prototype, superseded │\n ├─────────────────────────────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ schemas/candidate_set.schema.json │ No producer │\n ├─────────────────────────────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ schemas/evaluated_candidate_set.schema.json │ No producer │\n ├─────────────────────────────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ op_s4_candidate_evaluator.md │ Actor not used │\n ├─────────────────────────────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ op_s4_target_research_worker.md │ Actor not used │\n └─────────────────────────────────────────────┴───────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\n HISTORICAL / PROOF\n\n Completed plans — archive, don't delete.\n\n ┌────────────────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────────────┐\n │ File │ Category │\n ├────────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ S4_IMPLEMENTATION_PLAN.md │ Completed plan │\n ├────────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ S4_FOUNDATION_PLAN.md │ Completed plan │\n ├────────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ S4_SINGLE_TARGET_PROTOTYPE_PLAN.md │ Completed plan │\n ├────────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ S4_IMPLEMENTATION_CHECKLIST.md │ Completed checklist │\n ├────────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ S4_AGENT_MATERIALIZATION_PLAN.md │ Completed plan │\n ├────────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ S4_next_docs.md │ Completed todo │\n ├────────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ S4_schema_*.md (7 files) │ Schema documentation (may be historical) │\n └────────────────────────────────────┴──────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\n ---\n EXECUTION WAVES\n\n Wave 1 — Freeze Truth\n\n No file changes. Write the canonical architecture document.\n\n - Create S4_ARCHITECTURE_V2.md — expanded version of the architecture section above\n - Define: actor map, artifact map, credential surface, phase definitions\n - This becomes the single source of truth for all subsequent waves\n\n Wave 2 — Update Canonical Living Docs\n\n Update all docs that describe how S4 works today.\n\n - Rewrite S4_runtime_control_flow.md based on Wave 1 truth\n - Update S4_invocation_spec.md — supervisor_shell entry point, helper-direct pattern\n - Update S4_contracts_registry.md — remove dead contracts, add asset_materialization_report\n - Update contracts/operator_dispatch_contract.md — 2 active actors only\n - Update contracts/operator_registry.md — 2 active actors + deprecated list\n\n Wave 3 — Update Agent-Local Docs (both layers)\n\n Align both central docs AND materialized agent workspaces.\n\n Central docs (in S4/):\n - Update sm_s4_asset_research.md — pipeline description\n - Update op_s4_coverage_analyst.md — new artifact format\n - Update op_s4_pack_compiler.md — new artifact format\n - Update op_s4_target_builder.md — mark as deprecated/helper-direct\n\n Materialized agent workspaces (in .openclaw/agents/):\n - Update sm_s4_asset_research/OPERATIONS.md — current pipeline + delegation to supervisor_shell\n - Update op_s4_coverage_analyst/OPERATIONS.md + CONTRACT.md — new format\n - Update op_s4_pack_compiler/OPERATIONS.md + CONTRACT.md — new format\n - Add deprecation note to op_s4_target_builder/OPERATIONS.md — \"legacy-retained, not canonical\"\n\n Wave 4 — Historical Cleanup (gated)\n\n Move historical files to archive. Mark deprecated files.\n\n - Create S4/archive/ directory\n - Move completed plans to archive/\n - Move deprecated schema docs to archive/\n - Add # DEPRECATED — replaced by <new_file> header to candidate-for-removal .py files\n\n Removal gates (ALL 3 must be true before deletion):\n 1. One full E2E cycle S3→S4→B2 proven with new core on a different video (not Quitandinha)\n 2. grep -r confirms no import/runtime path references the deprecated files\n 3. Canonical docs from Waves 1-3 have been written and reviewed\n\n Wave 5 — Lessons / Replication\n\n Capture transferable knowledge.\n\n - Create S4_POSTMORTEM_AND_LESSONS.md:\n - 3 architectural eras (Brave/text → Gemini/KMS → GPT-5.4-nano/Serper)\n - Decisions reverted and why\n - Signals we should have seen earlier\n - Cost comparison ($0.14/video vs 30+ min of 429 storms)\n - Create S4_TROUBLESHOOTING.md:\n - 429 storms diagnosis and resolution\n - Label ambiguity → wrong search results\n - False unresolved in pack (legacy format mismatch)\n - OpenClaw session accumulation between videos\n - Windows: .cmd extensions, Unicode in print(), path encoding\n - Actor doing internal logic instead of calling helper\n - Create S4_REUSABLE_PATTERNS.md — mini-checklist for S5/S6:\n - Target consolidation pattern: when S3 outputs overlap, consolidate at the S3→SN boundary\n - Helper-direct substitution: when LLM actor mangles paths or invents logic, move to deterministic Python helper\n - Provider selection by operational reality: don't pick the cheapest model, pick the one with best RPM/reliability at your scale\n - Dual-format fallback: when replacing artifacts, read new format first, fall back to legacy\n - Video context injection: extract era/style/subject from script before generating queries or evaluating\n - Over-materialization warning signs: if >50% of actors end up as helper-direct, the sector was over-materialized\n\n Wave 6 — Reference + Runbook\n\n Operational documentation for day-to-day use.\n\n - Create S4_PIPELINE_REFERENCE.md — quick card: each .py file, inputs, outputs, dependencies\n - Create S4_OPERATIONAL_RUNBOOK.md — how to run, configure, costs, monitor, credentials\n\n Wave 7 — Memory + Skill/Checklist Updates\n\n Meta-learning capture.\n\n - Update Claude memory files (s4_complete_handoff.md, s4_visual_retrieval_refactor.md)\n - Update MEMORY.md index\n - Identify improvements to sector creation workflow/skill\n - Update sector materialization checklists based on S4 lessons\n - Document: when to stop materializing actors and collapse to helpers\n\n ---\n NEW DOCUMENTS SUMMARY\n\n ┌──────────────────────────────┬──────┬──────────────────────────────────────┐\n │ Document │ Wave │ Purpose │\n ├──────────────────────────────┼──────┼──────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ S4_ARCHITECTURE_V2.md │ 1 │ Canonical truth │\n ├──────────────────────────────┼──────┼──────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ S4_POSTMORTEM_AND_LESSONS.md │ 5 │ 3 eras, decisions, signals │\n ├──────────────────────────────┼──────┼──────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ S4_TROUBLESHOOTING.md │ 5 │ Failure modes, diagnostics │\n ├──────────────────────────────┼──────┼──────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ S4_REUSABLE_PATTERNS.md │ 5 │ Mini-checklist for S5/S6 replication │\n ├──────────────────────────────┼──────┼──────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ S4_PIPELINE_REFERENCE.md │ 6 │ Quick reference per .py file │\n ├──────────────────────────────┼──────┼──────────────────────────────────────┤\n │ S4_OPERATIONAL_RUNBOOK.md │ 6 │ Run, configure, costs, monitor │\n └──────────────────────────────┴──────┴──────────────────────────────────────┘\n\n ---"}],"timestamp":1775502219639}}
