{"type":"message","id":"16c5e88d","parentId":"9c593ab8","timestamp":"2026-04-07T10:35:07.449Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_glqThiszEpjnG5DKtklm2CFU|fc_06eabf5088e8d8890169d4ddd181548196b0eb1067f7c89f77","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\OpenClaw Workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S5\\S5_SCENE_KIT_OBJECTS_V1.md","edits":[{"oldText":"### Suggested V1 fields per family\n- `family_id`\n- `family_role`\n  - constrained but simple V1 values such as:\n    - `establishing`\n    - `supporting`\n    - `punctuating`\n- `family_label`\n  - short descriptive label\n- `editorial_purpose`\n  - short explanation of what this family enables in the cut\n- `priority`\n  - example values: `required`, `preferred`, `optional`\n- `target_asset_count`\n  - object with `minimum`, `ideal`, `maximum`\n- `grounding_strength`\n  - example values: `high`, `medium`, `low`\n- `creative_freedom_level`\n  - example values: `strict`, `controlled`, `moderate`, `open`\n- `preferred_generation_modes[]`\n- `reference_inputs[]`\n  - references from S4 or derived reference packages\n- `preserve_requirements[]`\n- `avoid_literal_copy_notes[]`\n- `family_notes`\n","newText":"### Suggested V1 fields per family\n- `family_id`\n- `family_type`\n  - constrained but practical V1 values such as:\n    - `hero`\n    - `support`\n    - `detail`\n    - `atmospheric`\n    - `transition`\n    - `fallback`\n- `family_label`\n  - short descriptive label\n- `priority`\n  - example values: `required`, `preferred`, `optional`\n- `target_asset_count`\n  - object with `minimum`, `ideal`, `maximum`\n- `grounding_strength`\n  - example values: `high`, `medium`, `low`\n- `creative_freedom_level`\n  - example values: `strict`, `controlled`, `moderate`, `open`\n- `preferred_generation_modes[]`\n- `reference_inputs[]`\n  - references from S4 or derived reference packages\n- `preserve_requirements[]`\n- `avoid_literal_copy_notes[]`\n- `editorial_notes`\n  - lightweight free-text downstream note\n- `family_notes`\n"},{"oldText":"V1 intentionally avoids too many fine-grained enums like:\n- detailed editorial energy scales\n- detailed timing use cases\n- overly nuanced visual function taxonomies\n\nThose may become useful later, but for now they are more likely to increase output instability than practical value.\n","newText":"V1 intentionally avoids too many fine-grained enums like:\n- detailed editorial energy scales\n- detailed timing use cases\n- overly nuanced visual function taxonomies\n- a separate heavy editorial role taxonomy beyond `family_type`\n\nThose may become useful later, but for now they are more likely to increase output instability than practical value.\n"}]},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\Desktop\\\\OpenClaw Workspace\\\\content_factory_block2\\\\S5\\\\S5_SCENE_KIT_OBJECTS_V1.md\",\"edits\":[{\"oldText\":\"### Suggested V1 fields per family\\n- `family_id`\\n- `family_role`\\n  - constrained but simple V1 values such as:\\n    - `establishing`\\n    - `supporting`\\n    - `punctuating`\\n- `family_label`\\n  - short descriptive label\\n- `editorial_purpose`\\n  - short explanation of what this family enables in the cut\\n- `priority`\\n  - example values: `required`, `preferred`, `optional`\\n- `target_asset_count`\\n  - object with `minimum`, `ideal`, `maximum`\\n- `grounding_strength`\\n  - example values: `high`, `medium`, `low`\\n- `creative_freedom_level`\\n  - example values: `strict`, `controlled`, `moderate`, `open`\\n- `preferred_generation_modes[]`\\n- `reference_inputs[]`\\n  - references from S4 or derived reference packages\\n- `preserve_requirements[]`\\n- `avoid_literal_copy_notes[]`\\n- `family_notes`\\n\",\"newText\":\"### Suggested V1 fields per family\\n- `family_id`\\n- `family_type`\\n  - constrained but practical V1 values such as:\\n    - `hero`\\n    - `support`\\n    - `detail`\\n    - `atmospheric`\\n    - `transition`\\n    - `fallback`\\n- `family_label`\\n  - short descriptive label\\n- `priority`\\n  - example values: `required`, `preferred`, `optional`\\n- `target_asset_count`\\n  - object with `minimum`, `ideal`, `maximum`\\n- `grounding_strength`\\n  - example values: `high`, `medium`, `low`\\n- `creative_freedom_level`\\n  - example values: `strict`, `controlled`, `moderate`, `open`\\n- `preferred_generation_modes[]`\\n- `reference_inputs[]`\\n  - references from S4 or derived reference packages\\n- `preserve_requirements[]`\\n- `avoid_literal_copy_notes[]`\\n- `editorial_notes`\\n  - lightweight free-text downstream note\\n- `family_notes`\\n\"},{\"oldText\":\"V1 intentionally avoids too many fine-grained enums like:\\n- detailed editorial energy scales\\n- detailed timing use cases\\n- overly nuanced visual function taxonomies\\n\\nThose may become useful later, but for now they are more likely to increase output instability than practical value.\\n\",\"newText\":\"V1 intentionally avoids too many fine-grained enums like:\\n- detailed editorial energy scales\\n- detailed timing use cases\\n- overly nuanced visual function taxonomies\\n- a separate heavy editorial role taxonomy beyond `family_type`\\n\\nThose may become useful later, but for now they are more likely to increase output instability than practical value.\\n\"}]}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":149,"output":663,"cacheRead":122368,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":123180,"cost":{"input":0.00037250000000000006,"output":0.009945,"cacheRead":0.030591999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0409095}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775558092239,"responseId":"resp_06eabf5088e8d8890169d4ddcfb2f481968809e6b664272b49"}}
